    "body": "Okay, so AFAICT, `web3.currentProvider.send` expects a callback to be passed.\r\n\r\nSee Synthetix and JoinColony's use of `web3.currentProvider` in their test helpers :\r\n\r\n+ [Synthetix helper example][1]\r\n+ [JoinColony helper example][2]\r\n\r\n[1]: https://github.com/Synthetixio/synthetix/blob/debf03c2afcc63607d4be3f7482ccc52e2c38e3c/test/utils/testUtils.js#L13-L19\r\n[2]: https://github.com/JoinColony/colonyNetwork/blob/c5ea3ab2320ffc196ade0a154195ba0ec16a3620/helpers/test-helper.js#L102-L116\r\n\r\nIt would be pretty useful to document this. We can likely also do some things on our end to enable not having to pass a callback.",
